{"id":278,"date":"2024-03-24T15:55:37","date_gmt":"2024-03-24T15:55:37","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/?page_id=278"},"modified":"2024-04-16T10:39:09","modified_gmt":"2024-04-16T10:39:09","slug":"ap-1ere-annee","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/ap-1ere-annee\/","title":{"rendered":"AP-1\u00e8re-Ann\u00e9e"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Actions Professionnelles 1\u00e8re Ann\u00e9e<\/h2>\n\n\n<style>.wp-block-kadence-spacer.kt-block-spacer-278_b6d908-cc .kt-block-spacer{height:6px;}.wp-block-kadence-spacer.kt-block-spacer-278_b6d908-cc .kt-divider{border-top-width:5px;height:1px;border-top-color:#0083ff;width:75%;border-top-style:solid;}<\/style>\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-spacer aligncenter kt-block-spacer-278_b6d908-cc\"><div class=\"kt-block-spacer kt-block-spacer-halign-center\"><hr class=\"kt-divider\"\/><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Sur cette page vous trouverez tout les projets que j\u2019ai effectu\u00e9s durant ma premi\u00e8re ann\u00e9e de BTS SIO.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:0;padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--80);padding-bottom:0;padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--80)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-constrained wp-block-column-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Projets Nolark<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Le projet NOLARK fut entrepris durant ma premi\u00e8re ann\u00e9e de BTS. Il se mat\u00e9rialisa sous la forme d&rsquo;un site web sp\u00e9cialis\u00e9 dans la commercialisation de casques de motos. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Pour mener \u00e0 bien ce projet, nous avons eu recours a NetBeans, un environnement de d\u00e9veloppement int\u00e9gr\u00e9 (IDE) offrant une panoplie d&rsquo;outils facilitant la cr\u00e9ation de pages web. Ce logiciel m&rsquo;a permis de construire le site depuis le d\u00e9but, en me concentrant principalement sur les langages HTML et CSS. Gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 ces langages, j&rsquo;ai pu \u00e9laborer une plateforme fonctionnelle et esth\u00e9tique, r\u00e9pondant aux cahier des charge sp\u00e9cifiques du projet NOLARK.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">&nbsp;<strong>Comp\u00e9tences d\u00e9velopp\u00e9es :<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>1.3 D\u00e9velopper la pr\u00e9sence en ligne de l\u2019organisation<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"has-medium-font-size wp-block-list\">\n<li>Participer \u00e0 la valorisation de l\u2019image de l\u2019organisation sur les m\u00e9dias num\u00e9riques en tenant compte du cadre juridique et des enjeux \u00e9conomiques<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>R\u00e9f\u00e9rencer les services en ligne de l\u2019organisation et mesurer leur visibilit\u00e9<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Participer \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9volution d\u2019un site Web exploitant les donn\u00e9es de l\u2019organisation<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>1.4 Travailler en mode projet<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"has-medium-font-size wp-block-list\">\n<li>Analyser les objectifs et les modalit\u00e9s d\u2019organisation d\u2019un projet<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Planifier les activit\u00e9s<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\">\u00c9valuer les indicateurs de suivi d\u2019un projet et analyser les \u00e9cart<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>1.5 Mettre \u00e0 disposition des utilisateurs un service informatique<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"has-medium-font-size wp-block-list\">\n<li>R\u00e9aliser les tests d\u2019int\u00e9gration et d\u2019acceptation d\u2019un service<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>D\u00e9ployer un service<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Accompagner les utilisateurs dans la mise en place d\u2019un service<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"690\" height=\"881\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-24_165833658.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-284\" style=\"width:617px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-24_165833658.png 690w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-24_165833658-235x300.png 235w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n<style>.wp-block-kadence-spacer.kt-block-spacer-278_87fcdc-16 .kt-block-spacer{height:6px;}.wp-block-kadence-spacer.kt-block-spacer-278_87fcdc-16 .kt-divider{border-top-width:5px;height:1px;border-top-color:#0083ff;width:75%;border-top-style:solid;}<\/style>\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-spacer aligncenter kt-block-spacer-278_87fcdc-16\"><div class=\"kt-block-spacer kt-block-spacer-halign-center\"><hr class=\"kt-divider\"\/><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--80);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--80)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"padding-right:0;padding-left:0\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Projets RLE<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Cr\u00e9ation d\u2019un RLE (R\u00e9seau Local d\u2019Entreprise)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Pour mener \u00e0 bien ce projet, j&rsquo;ai du me munir de VirtualBox afin de cr\u00e9er un r\u00e9seaux informatique compos\u00e9 d&rsquo;un routeur sous Debian, un serveur GLPI &amp; FusionInventory et 2 client sous Windows<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">&nbsp;<strong>Comp\u00e9tences d\u00e9velopp\u00e9es <\/strong>:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>1.5 Mettre \u00e0 disposition des utilisateurs un service informatique :<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\">R\u00e9aliser les tests d\u2019int\u00e9gration et d\u2019acceptation d\u2019un service<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\">D\u00e9ployer un service<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Accompagner les utilisateurs dans la mise en place d\u2019un service<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"282\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-638\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image-3.png 600w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image-3-300x141.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<style>.wp-block-kadence-spacer.kt-block-spacer-278_d09155-39 .kt-block-spacer{height:20px;}.wp-block-kadence-spacer.kt-block-spacer-278_d09155-39 .kt-divider{border-top-width:5px;height:1px;border-top-color:#0083ff;width:75%;border-top-style:solid;}<\/style>\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-spacer aligncenter kt-block-spacer-278_d09155-39\"><div class=\"kt-block-spacer kt-block-spacer-halign-center\"><hr class=\"kt-divider\"\/><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-3 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--80);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--80)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Nextcloud<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Pour le 2\u00e8me Semestre de Premi\u00e8re Ann\u00e9e, nous avons fait en Action Professionnelle un projet individuel sur une solution de sauvegarde.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Dans mon cas j&rsquo;ai d\u00e9cider de choisir Nextcloud que j&rsquo;ai autoh\u00e9berger sous machine virtuel Debian, une solution open source de stockage et de partage de fichiers bas\u00e9e sur le cloud. Con\u00e7ue pour offrir aux utilisateurs un contr\u00f4le total sur leurs donn\u00e9es, Nextcloud permet de cr\u00e9er un espace de stockage s\u00e9curis\u00e9 et personnalisable, accessible depuis n&rsquo;importe quel appareil connect\u00e9 \u00e0 Internet.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Comp\u00e9tences d\u00e9velopp\u00e9es :<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>1.5 Mettre \u00e0 disposition des utilisateurs un service informatique :<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\">R\u00e9aliser les tests d\u2019int\u00e9gration et d\u2019acceptation d\u2019un service<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\">D\u00e9ployer un service<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Accompagner les utilisateurs dans la mise en place d\u2019un service<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>1.6 Organiser son d\u00e9veloppement professionnel avec comme sous comp\u00e9tences :<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Mettre en place son environnement d\u2019apprentissage personnel<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\">G\u00e9rer son identit\u00e9 professionnelle<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\">D\u00e9velopper son projet professionnel<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-24_170647159-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-290\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-24_170647159-1024x576.png 1024w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-24_170647159-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-24_170647159-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-24_170647159-1536x864.png 1536w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-24_170647159.png 1920w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-large-font-size\"><strong>Ma Documentation Nextcloud<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div data-wp-interactive=\"core\/file\" class=\"wp-block-file\"><object data-wp-bind--hidden=\"!state.hasPdfPreview\" hidden class=\"wp-block-file__embed\" data=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/DOCUMENTATION-NEXTCLOUD-3.pdf\" type=\"application\/pdf\" style=\"width:100%;height:600px\" aria-label=\"Contenu embarqu\u00e9 DOCUMENTATION-NEXTCLOUD.\"><\/object><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-b2e81ca1-7147-486b-b19c-0de017a1ccf4\" href=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/DOCUMENTATION-NEXTCLOUD-3.pdf\">DOCUMENTATION-NEXTCLOUD<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/DOCUMENTATION-NEXTCLOUD-3.pdf\" class=\"wp-block-file__button wp-element-button\" download aria-describedby=\"wp-block-file--media-b2e81ca1-7147-486b-b19c-0de017a1ccf4\">T\u00e9l\u00e9charger<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Actions Professionnelles 1\u00e8re Ann\u00e9e Sur cette page vous trouverez tout les projets que j\u2019ai effectu\u00e9s durant ma premi\u00e8re ann\u00e9e de BTS SIO. Projets Nolark Le projet NOLARK fut entrepris d